"predisposta come sottopagina separata."
msgstr ""
"This page remains the quick access point for the function. Practical details are collected in "
"[Overview](lin-fit/panoramica.md), while [How it works](lin-fit/funzionamento.md) is prepared as "
"a separate subpage."

